{
  "stem": "1975.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 214.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in order to go to Italy, I had to have my diploma from the gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was one of the reasons that I have not traveled back to my city.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was waiting to get the diploma.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we have finished our studies in the beginning of June.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as days went by, and for some reason, the diploma was issued to the later part of June, June 20, June 19 or June 20.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have also had, since the Russians came in, they have changed the political structure and the living structure in the country.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They have first of all assessed-- they start taking many people to-- to the-- to Siberia, those people who they felt they are bourgeois, that they are rich and they have businesses, and they're exploiters.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And by calling them bourgeois and exploiters, of the proletarians, they have taken out a big, large number of Jews whom they considered exploiters, and they took them to Siberia to get the families.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And their businesses were taken over by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We, ourselves, in school, we had the opportunity in few occasions-- they would send us to nationalize some businesses, where we had to take inventories.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And unfortunately, we felt very bad for the owners who suddenly, they became just nobody.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would not let them even into the business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This happened also in the small villages.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father, my family had also-- we were pretty wealthy of the standards at that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my parents were also the least to being taken, taken-- taken away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But in fact, my father was in a very excellent relationship with the-- with the clergy and some other friends.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they have helped him to-- to be taken off the least at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
